      "comment": "HOLLY MAGIC (6) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth (22.25) in a Grade 4 at this track. Form here at the trip sound including three wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Tough to beat if on-song. LOVELY MADELINE (3) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fifth by 4.5 lengths (22.64). Strong form has emerged from her last run. Should be about the money. AUSSIE AUDI (2) was in the minors two back (22.20) at this track but ran below best last time there, finishing 6th. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. EMMY PANAMA (1) can sneak into the finish.",
